  "reference_number": "RUS1356",
  "remarks": "\n JSC Kalashnikov Concern is a Russian weapons manufacturer which has supplied products used by the Russian army in Ukraine. JSC Kalashnikov Concern has therefore provided goods or technology to a person who is responsible for, engages in, provides support for, or promotes policies or actions which destabilise Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. In addition, a Russian state-owned defence conglomerate, Rostec State Corporation, also owns 25% plus one of the shares of JSC Kalashnikov Concern and so they are an involved person through carrying on business as a Government of Russia-affiliated entity.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
